data.description: WELCOME HOME  to this spacious and spectacular home nestled in the Valley Forge community off O'Conner Rd and near IH 35.  This extraordinary home has 3 living areas for entertaining and much enjoyment. This home boasts a large living/dining room, family room with fireplace and enclosed huge patio with connections for outdoor TV viewing.  Just think of that next gathering in this terrific home!! There will be cheers throughout the house when the next favorite team game is on. Come enjoy the spectacular front and back yards with ample mature trees. Enjoy starting your own garden. There is plenty of room.  Updated granite in bathroom vanity and windows throughout the home. Come and see it for yourself and get ready to make a deal! You're gonna love this tranquil, quiet location tucked away in this quiet established community.
